    • ENCLOSE_VALUE_SQL

      public static final String ENCLOSE_VALUE_SQL
      SQL character enclosing a table cell returned by injection. It allows to detect the correct end of a table cell data during parsing. Expected schema of a table cell data is 
      %04[table cell]%05[number of occurrences]%04
